abstract: An aide to Senator Cory Booker shared on Twitter a picture of staff aides carrying 10 large pizzas into the Senate.
lead_paragraph: With no end in sight for the debate over amendments, senators appeared to be growing more frustrated with the limitations of the trial. As the Senate reconvened, about a third of its members were late to return, straggling into the chamber.
keywords: Trump-Ukraine Whistle-blower Complaint and Impeachment Inquiry
